        {
            "title": "警灣仔搜住所檢6萬元毒品 36歲外籍女涉販毒被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"被捕女子帶署調查。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3773df982bd000ebd3ec98cd87b55333/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011010565125380.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">被捕女子帶署調查。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>港島總區反三合會行動組人員根據線報及經深入調查後，昨日（9日）在灣仔展開打擊毒品行動。人員昨日下午約6時突擊搜查灣仔一住宅單位，在單位內檢獲約178克懷疑大麻、21克懷疑可卡因及190克懷疑含四氫大麻酚的糖果。人員遂以涉嫌「販毒」拘捕一名36歲外籍女子。行動中檢獲的毒品總市值約6萬元。被捕人現正被扣留調查。案件仍在調查中。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4008766/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示檢獲的毒品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7ec6d7cf145166bc0cf09d1b3477c726/2025-01/Trafficking_in_DD_Team_1_RATU_HKI_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示檢獲的毒品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方提醒市民，特別是青少年，應時刻保持警覺，切勿以身試法。警方重申，藏有及販運危險藥物均屬嚴重罪行。根據香港法例第134章《危險藥物條例》，任何人藏有或販運危險藥物，一經定罪，最高可被判處罰款一百萬元及監禁七年或罰款七百萬元及終身監禁。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046265/即時-港聞-警灣仔搜住所檢6萬元毒品-36歲外籍女涉販毒被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 11:01:00",
            "source": "stheadline",
